&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;관련 글&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;a href=&quot;http://macnews.tistory.com/3386&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;맥용 'Boom 2'와 연동되는 iOS용 리모트 앱 무료 배포&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;a href=&quot;http://macnews.tistory.com/2849&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;맥용 이퀄라이저 프로그램 'Boom 2' 정식 출시&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;a href=&quot;http://macnews.tistory.com/1038&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;시스템 전체에 걸쳐 이퀄라이저(EQ)를 적용할 수 있는 방법&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/image/235FCA41577A632924BEE0&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/deed.ko&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;저작자 표시&quot; src=&quot;http://i1.daumcdn.net/cfs.tistory/resource/4864/static/admin/editor/ccl_black01.png&quot;/&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;비영리&quot; src=&quot;http://i1.daumcdn.net/cfs.tistory/resource/4864/static/admin/editor/ccl_black02.png&quot;/&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;변경 금지&quot; src=&quot;http://i1.daumcdn.net/cfs.tistory/resource/4864/static/admin/editor/ccl_black03.png&quot;/&gt;
